Phase 4: Project Planning Phase
Milestones:

Week 1: Environment setup and API key integration.

Week 2: Development of the Multimodal prompt-engineering strategy.

Week 3: Implementation of the Streamlit frontend and error-handling logic.

Week 4: Testing with various vehicle types (Cruisers, Sportbikes, EVs).

Risk Management: Identified "API Overload" as a primary risk. Mitigation: Implemented a 3-attempt retry loop with time.sleep().
